com.rockhoppertech.music.midi.js

Class KeySignature

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.rockhoppertech.music.midi.js.KeySignature
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class KeySignature
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Data follows MIDI file format for key signatures. 
       FF 59 02 sf mi
    sf = -7 for 7 flats, -1 for 1 flat, etc, 0 for key of c, 1 for 1 sharp, etc. mi = 0 for major, 1 for minor It's serializable in order to drag and drop notelists.
    Author:
    Gene De Lisa
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
